{"tid":674650,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"你預期幾時會出現港鐵行乞黨？","createTime":"2018-05-23T01:24:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-24T02:46:11.000Z","uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"67a7783af55b27cdb0d9acb963ed7ad85015ec35","tid":674650,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T01:24:16.000Z","msg":"鑑於香港開始出現極端嘅行乞手法<br />\n<br />\n令我諗起中國嘅地鐵行乞黨，通常兩人一組，前面嗰個一路唱啲慘情歌，拖住後面嗰個，後面嗰個通常就係好老好慘咁嘅<br />\n<br />\n雖然話港鐵唔准行乞，但係經過最近嘅垃圾桶同棵樹，大家都明，凡事唔係絕對嘅<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你預期幾時香港會出現港鐵行乞黨呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d53478df53519c8ac125417504dd69005a6fbc9","tid":674650,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T01:31:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8cb6ec95bb97577fc53dd2b5ae00a9e41138b975","tid":674650,"uid":8048,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T01:35:14.000Z","msg":"想當年係中環站<br />\n有個阿嬸過嚟問我可唔可以借錢俾佢坐車<br />\n我就問返佢點入閘<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01156b93e615e6eb2a9a00b96cfba8b8fcf83b12","tid":674650,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8cb6ec95bb97577fc53dd2b5ae00a9e41138b975","tid":674650,"uid":8048,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T01:35:14.000Z","msg":"想當年係中環站<br />\n有個阿嬸過嚟問我可唔可以借錢俾佢坐車<br />\n我就問返佢點入閘<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T01:37:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  識玩"},{"pid":"df9aff17b9d90f98d30ae33fcab6fca9f2f3d4df","tid":674650,"uid":174191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8cb6ec95bb97577fc53dd2b5ae00a9e41138b975","tid":674650,"uid":8048,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T01:35:14.000Z","msg":"想當年係中環站<br />\n有個阿嬸過嚟問我可唔可以借錢俾佢坐車<br />\n我就問返佢點入閘<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T01:45:28